WEBVTT

00:23.550 --> 00:24.280
Master.

00:25.670 --> 00:26.530
Lejun is awake.

00:29.920 --> 00:31.550
Lejun told me a story,

00:32.470 --> 00:34.110
but it's too bizarre.

00:35.110 --> 00:36.310
It's hard to believe.

00:36.880 --> 00:38.740
I hope you could clarify it for me.

00:41.000 --> 00:41.920
Lejun said

00:43.110 --> 00:44.670
I'm not Prince Qi's son

00:46.880 --> 00:48.640
but your son.

00:53.520 --> 00:54.280
Is it true?

02:30.550 --> 02:34.710
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:34.900 --> 02:37.670
[Episode 17]

02:51.750 --> 02:52.470
Take a rest.

02:53.120 --> 02:55.030
Have some ginseng soup
to strengthen your body.

02:55.030 --> 02:56.870
It'll be another tough few days.

02:57.960 --> 02:58.760
Fortunately,

02:59.030 --> 03:01.230
the ointment Ruisheng made works well.

03:01.630 --> 03:03.430
The swelling has gone down a lot.

03:04.260 --> 03:06.520
How could the Grand Tutor bear to do this?

03:14.710 --> 03:15.400
And this.

03:16.310 --> 03:18.240
Anmin asked me to bring this to you.

03:18.470 --> 03:20.360
He said he has nothing to offer

03:21.240 --> 03:22.360
but an abundance of soft cushions

03:22.360 --> 03:23.960
that can make sitting and kneeling

03:23.960 --> 03:25.020
more comfortable.

03:25.079 --> 03:26.750
Pad your knees with this.

03:27.079 --> 03:28.210
It'll ease the pain.

03:30.520 --> 03:31.280
Don't worry.

03:31.630 --> 03:34.490
Prince Jing'an's Mansion
will always be your home.

03:34.910 --> 03:36.079
You can stay here

03:36.630 --> 03:37.690
as long as you want.

03:51.870 --> 03:52.930
Thank you, Yuanji.

03:54.560 --> 03:55.360
And Anmin too.

04:01.680 --> 04:03.560
My Lady, it's cold at night.

04:03.750 --> 04:04.810
Don't catch a cold.

04:05.120 --> 04:06.560
Isn't this the fox fur cloak
His Highness hunted

04:06.560 --> 04:08.030
and made himself a few years ago?

04:08.030 --> 04:09.760
His Highness asked me to get it.

04:10.680 --> 04:12.410
Why didn't he bring it himself?

04:17.040 --> 04:18.300
And this ointment too.

04:18.950 --> 04:20.720
He requested Ruisheng to

04:20.720 --> 04:21.579
make it for you,

04:22.190 --> 04:23.920
but he just won't come himself.

04:24.160 --> 04:24.950
Maybe

04:26.070 --> 04:27.310
he's afraid to see me.

04:28.680 --> 04:29.270
What?

04:33.240 --> 04:33.800
Nothing.

04:34.950 --> 04:35.720
Yuanji,

04:36.360 --> 04:37.960
I can keep watch here myself.

04:38.120 --> 04:39.450
Please go back and rest.

04:49.480 --> 04:50.740
Take care of yourself.

05:12.870 --> 05:17.070
When the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world.

05:17.870 --> 05:19.160
How are the Phoenix Heart Tokens

05:19.160 --> 05:20.490
linked to the minerals?

05:29.750 --> 05:30.610
Your Highness,

05:30.750 --> 05:32.870
I bought the pear blossom candy
from Chengyi Hall.

05:32.870 --> 05:34.130
Deliver it to Lady Xie.

05:34.630 --> 05:35.920
I heard she's been keeping vigil
for 3 days,

05:35.920 --> 05:36.950
eaten or drunk nothing

05:36.950 --> 05:38.409
except some ginseng soup.

05:38.430 --> 05:39.960
Aren't you going to see her?

05:40.120 --> 05:41.070
Consort Yuanji and Madam Ruisheng

05:41.070 --> 05:42.000
visit her often.

05:42.270 --> 05:43.190
You're at least Lady Xie's

05:43.190 --> 05:44.120
husband in name,

05:44.270 --> 05:45.530
and haven't divorced.

05:45.680 --> 05:46.920
It's understandable for you to

05:46.920 --> 05:48.310
observe mourning for her.

05:48.310 --> 05:50.310
I doubt she wants to see me right now.

05:51.430 --> 05:52.290
Then this time,

05:53.000 --> 05:55.130
shall I ask the Princess to deliver it?

05:57.310 --> 05:58.000
Hang on.

06:07.510 --> 06:08.370
Your Highness.

06:13.270 --> 06:14.130
Is she alright?

06:14.310 --> 06:15.770
My Lady has fallen asleep.

06:18.480 --> 06:20.080
Please keep your voice down.

06:20.310 --> 06:21.910
My Lady finally fell asleep.

06:29.800 --> 06:31.530
She'd been staying up for days.

06:31.750 --> 06:33.560
Consort Yuanji and Madam Ruisheng were

06:33.560 --> 06:35.159
worried that My Lady
couldn't endure the strain

06:35.159 --> 06:36.620
so soon after her illness.

06:36.630 --> 06:39.430
Consort Yuanji just
brought a bowl of calming soup

06:39.750 --> 06:42.360
and tricked My Lady into drinking it
as ginseng soup.

06:42.360 --> 06:44.240
Now she's finally asleep.

06:46.750 --> 06:48.010
How can she sleep here?

06:49.800 --> 06:51.190
I'll carry her back to rest.

06:51.190 --> 06:52.630
Back... Back where?

06:56.040 --> 06:56.680
My Lady...

07:11.600 --> 07:14.120
It seems the outcome of our bet
is decided.

07:15.480 --> 07:16.410
I'm going to win.

07:16.430 --> 07:17.430
That's not right.

07:18.190 --> 07:21.120
I remember betting that
they'd end up together.

07:21.260 --> 07:23.190
You always win bets with your husband

07:23.190 --> 07:25.160
because you never own up
when you lose, right?

07:25.160 --> 07:26.090
That's not true!

07:28.000 --> 07:30.240
Fine, I'll let you have your way.

07:30.800 --> 07:32.470
How about letting Ziqi study

07:32.680 --> 07:34.430
both literature or medicine?

07:35.560 --> 07:36.690
I think that's good.

07:36.750 --> 07:37.350
By the way,

07:37.750 --> 07:39.310
didn't you say His Highness
got injured

07:39.310 --> 07:40.680
while getting bear gall

07:40.680 --> 07:41.430
for Jiayu?

07:42.190 --> 07:43.680
Can he carry someone now?

07:43.950 --> 07:44.680
Don't worry.

07:45.190 --> 07:46.250
He won't feel pain.

07:46.390 --> 07:47.000
True.

07:47.950 --> 07:50.920
Do you think Qing Long likes Yan Yue

07:50.920 --> 07:51.950
or Nanxing?

07:52.750 --> 07:53.750
I bet it's Yan Yue.

07:53.750 --> 07:54.870
More bets?

08:26.360 --> 08:31.530
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

08:32.360 --> 08:36.039
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

08:36.059 --> 08:40.260
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

08:40.380 --> 08:42.850
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

08:42.870 --> 08:45.850
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

08:45.880 --> 08:49.630
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

08:49.650 --> 08:52.340
♪ I shall never forget ♪

08:52.430 --> 08:56.820
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

08:56.840 --> 09:00.270
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

09:00.300 --> 09:03.080
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

09:03.110 --> 09:06.110
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

09:06.130 --> 09:10.180
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

09:10.210 --> 09:13.690
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

09:13.720 --> 09:16.640
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

09:16.660 --> 09:22.190
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

10:07.750 --> 10:10.880
This Phoenix Heart Token is
different from my mother's.

10:16.550 --> 10:18.790
If it's not with him, then...

10:22.200 --> 10:23.800
Why did you sigh with relief?

10:25.030 --> 10:27.200
I don't have Her Highness's
Phoenix Heart Token.

10:27.200 --> 10:29.730
I didn't kill Her Highness.
Someone else did.

10:30.270 --> 10:31.130
Who could it be?

10:33.030 --> 10:34.560
Xie Jiayu, you're so smart.

10:34.720 --> 10:36.780
You must already have an idea, right?

10:36.910 --> 10:37.570
Besides me,

10:37.670 --> 10:38.840
of those by Her Highness's side,

10:38.840 --> 10:40.970
who could do it and had a reason to do it?

10:41.790 --> 10:44.050
How many suspects are still in your list?

10:47.000 --> 10:49.150
If not me, it must be her

10:49.870 --> 10:50.630
or them.

10:52.600 --> 10:54.600
You should be angry, furious,

10:54.910 --> 10:55.670
or confused.

10:56.550 --> 10:58.280
So why did you sigh with relief?

11:05.200 --> 11:06.800
You're relieved it isn't me,

11:07.840 --> 11:08.550
aren't you?

11:10.670 --> 11:11.200
Yaoyao,

11:13.840 --> 11:14.910
why do you feel so?

11:24.480 --> 11:25.270
Xiao Wuyi,

11:25.670 --> 11:27.870
you're not completely in the clear yet.

11:28.600 --> 11:29.960
Since you already knew my motive,

11:29.960 --> 11:31.630
you could've hidden my mother's token

11:31.630 --> 11:32.560
somewhere else.

11:37.270 --> 11:38.440
If you suspect it's me,

11:38.440 --> 11:40.170
you can take my life at any time.

11:48.300 --> 11:49.560
Do you think I dare not?

12:05.960 --> 12:07.960
If I confess my love to you right now,

12:08.030 --> 12:09.690
would you think I'm a lunatic?

12:12.840 --> 12:13.840
You are a lunatic.

12:17.120 --> 12:17.850
Xie Jiayu...

12:22.510 --> 12:23.840
My heart belongs to you.

12:32.320 --> 12:32.910
I know...

12:34.310 --> 12:36.530
♪ Weave our devotion
into a melody of two hearts ♪

12:34.550 --> 12:36.560
I know what Her Highness means to you.

12:36.560 --> 12:38.850
♪ Mirror a gaze of stars and moon ♪

12:38.600 --> 12:40.440
I'd never hurt the mother
of the woman I love.

12:39.560 --> 12:42.830
♪ Forever illuminate each other's nights ♪

12:42.390 --> 12:43.150
Never.

12:44.690 --> 12:47.210
♪ The truest, most profound affection ♪

12:47.230 --> 12:49.230
♪ An eternal vow ♪

12:49.630 --> 12:54.030
♪ To be each other's forever ♪

12:54.780 --> 12:59.080
♪ You enter my dreams,
permeating the crevices of my heart ♪

12:59.340 --> 13:01.340
♪ Every inch of longing ♪

13:01.360 --> 13:05.080
♪ Tugs at unspeakable fantasies ♪

13:05.100 --> 13:09.210
♪ Know that your heart is my heart ♪

13:05.600 --> 13:06.360
You're hurt?

13:09.580 --> 13:11.830
♪ Cherishing each other ♪

13:09.870 --> 13:10.730
What happened?

13:11.270 --> 13:12.910
You didn't have this at Lingfeng Fort.

13:11.850 --> 13:16.440
♪ We will never be alone ♪

13:13.080 --> 13:13.540
What...

13:17.840 --> 13:19.600
♪ In the endless stream of time ♪

13:19.620 --> 13:22.460
♪ My life's every wish is for you ♪

13:22.480 --> 13:27.440
♪ All the sweet nothings in the world
fall short ♪

13:28.280 --> 13:29.960
♪ As time flows gently ♪

13:29.980 --> 13:32.600
♪ Hold each other and seal our vows ♪

13:32.620 --> 13:34.160
♪ Whatever the path ♪

13:34.180 --> 13:38.440
♪ I just want to be with you
for all time ♪

13:38.730 --> 13:40.320
♪ A lifelong promise ♪

13:40.350 --> 13:43.010
♪ My life's every moment is for you ♪

13:43.030 --> 13:45.030
♪ After all of it ♪

13:45.060 --> 13:47.880
♪ May all your dreams be realized ♪

13:48.910 --> 13:50.280
♪ Just you and me ♪

13:50.310 --> 13:53.490
♪ From dawn to dusk, year after year ♪

13:53.760 --> 13:59.640
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

14:01.830 --> 14:12.290
♪ Hand in hand, let's experience
the bittersweet flavors of earthly life ♪

14:33.500 --> 14:36.710
[Memorial tablet of
the late Princess Li Yunzhao]

14:34.030 --> 14:34.750
Mother,

14:35.360 --> 14:36.790
if you're watching from heaven,

14:36.790 --> 14:37.910
please bless me

14:39.510 --> 14:40.910
to find the culprit soon.

14:46.240 --> 14:47.370
Someone made a move.

14:49.040 --> 14:49.630
Who?

14:50.840 --> 14:53.240
Silly brother, let's go see Father.

14:53.790 --> 14:55.480
Yes, let's go see Father.

15:06.480 --> 15:08.090
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

15:10.080 --> 15:10.960
Memorials impeaching you

15:10.960 --> 15:12.560
are flooding the Censorate.

15:13.080 --> 15:14.740
Still won't hand Cui Jun over?

15:15.720 --> 15:17.120
The prison cart is making its way.

15:17.120 --> 15:18.960
It rained and there was a landslide.

15:18.960 --> 15:20.510
Traveling on the mountain is slow.

15:20.510 --> 15:22.110
Don't give me that nonsense.

15:22.120 --> 15:24.080
I've known that
Cui Jun had arrived in Jiankang.

15:24.080 --> 15:25.670
He was just secretly imprisoned by you.

15:25.670 --> 15:27.130
Even if I hand over Cui Jun,

15:27.390 --> 15:29.790
the nobles won't try to
impeach me any less.

15:31.390 --> 15:33.240
You're just a witness
in the Cui Family Case,

15:33.240 --> 15:35.000
escorting the Cui prisoners on the way.

15:35.000 --> 15:36.000
Once in Jiankang,

15:36.000 --> 15:38.120
you have to hand them over
to the Court of Judicial Review.

15:38.120 --> 15:40.030
Do you really want to
pocket the Phoenix Heart Token

15:40.030 --> 15:41.760
and the Cui family's minerals?

15:42.630 --> 15:45.960
Did Her Highness's death
really have nothing to do with you?

15:47.440 --> 15:48.120
Seriously?

15:51.030 --> 15:52.230
It's not what I think.

15:52.510 --> 15:55.000
It's a rumor in the court,

15:55.510 --> 15:58.240
saying Her Highness's death
wasn't an accident,

15:58.320 --> 15:59.670
but that you murdered her

15:59.670 --> 16:00.730
to seize her token.

16:01.510 --> 16:03.170
If you don't hand over Cui Jun,

16:03.360 --> 16:04.840
the rumors will just worsen

16:04.840 --> 16:06.120
with each passing day.

16:06.440 --> 16:07.910
The nobles are watching you like a hawk,

16:07.910 --> 16:09.970
hoping to catch you slip up in any way.

16:10.720 --> 16:11.750
Cui Jun hasn't confessed

16:11.750 --> 16:13.010
how to crack the token,

16:13.360 --> 16:14.690
so I can't hand him over.

16:14.840 --> 16:16.550
Yan Yue said that be it Zhuyou hypnosis,

16:16.550 --> 16:17.670
poison, or torture,

16:17.670 --> 16:18.800
he didn't say a word.

16:19.270 --> 16:21.550
The spy trained by
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

16:21.550 --> 16:22.810
is indeed a character.

16:23.790 --> 16:26.320
Why is it you reporting this?
Where's Yan Yue?

16:29.120 --> 16:29.920
What's wrong?

16:47.630 --> 16:48.490
Your Highness.

16:49.360 --> 16:50.290
What's going on?

16:51.630 --> 16:53.390
Lady Xie said she wants to
work on her martial arts,

16:53.390 --> 16:55.590
that mourning is no reason to slack off.

16:55.790 --> 16:57.520
What did she eat for breakfast?

16:57.960 --> 16:58.490
Nothing.

16:59.390 --> 17:00.270
Lady Xie heard that

17:00.270 --> 17:02.120
you do it on an empty stomach
early in the morning,

17:02.120 --> 17:03.120
and insisted on doing the same.

17:03.120 --> 17:03.720
Nonsense!

17:07.589 --> 17:08.109
Jiayu!

17:09.240 --> 17:09.750
Jiayu.

17:11.109 --> 17:13.109
Trying to starve yourself to death?

17:15.960 --> 17:16.819
What happened?

17:18.560 --> 17:19.480
Nothing.

17:25.960 --> 17:26.560
Have this.

17:36.240 --> 17:38.170
Learning martial arts takes time.

17:38.510 --> 17:40.170
It's good if you want to train.

17:40.590 --> 17:42.350
But you have to take it step by step,

17:42.350 --> 17:44.350
instead of rushing it, understand?

17:44.440 --> 17:46.300
I just want to have something to do

17:47.280 --> 17:48.740
so my mind can stop racing.

17:50.000 --> 17:50.680
Xie Jiayu.

17:54.440 --> 17:56.040
Stop mistreating yourself.

17:59.780 --> 18:01.640
You said your heart belongs to me.

18:02.880 --> 18:03.920
Then would you

18:05.200 --> 18:06.260
kill for me as well?

18:06.960 --> 18:08.830
Princess Yunzhao just passed away.

18:08.830 --> 18:11.030
But if you can't pull yourself together,

18:11.030 --> 18:13.490
no one else can be
responsible for your life.

18:14.920 --> 18:15.750
Not even you?

18:17.290 --> 18:18.440
I can kill for you.

18:20.130 --> 18:22.590
But I can't help you
overcome this obstacle.

18:23.920 --> 18:25.510
You already know who did it,

18:26.880 --> 18:27.480
don't you?

18:32.350 --> 18:33.750
Bad news, Your Highness!

18:34.200 --> 18:35.460
Cui Jun was taken away!

18:37.590 --> 18:38.200
What?

18:38.350 --> 18:41.440
The kidnapper left a message on the wall,
saying they were

18:41.440 --> 18:43.640
acting on Crown Prince Wenxi's orders.

18:43.640 --> 18:44.370
Impossible.

18:45.670 --> 18:47.530
Don't go out for the next few days,

18:47.550 --> 18:48.240
OK?

19:06.880 --> 19:07.480
My Lady.

19:08.680 --> 19:10.210
The Heir arranged all this.

19:11.750 --> 19:14.550
He said although you're
not a real married couple,

19:14.640 --> 19:15.970
etiquette comes first.

19:16.070 --> 19:18.160
Princess Yunzhao is considered
half an elder to him.

19:18.160 --> 19:19.160
For the mourning,

19:19.270 --> 19:21.160
the estate should show its respects.

19:21.160 --> 19:23.360
The entire estate will mourn
by wearing

19:23.640 --> 19:24.700
mourning clothes.

19:24.750 --> 19:26.070
We've reported this
to the Dowager Princess,

19:26.070 --> 19:27.130
and she has agreed.

19:27.510 --> 19:28.400
I just wonder

19:28.680 --> 19:30.200
why the Heir took so long to

19:30.760 --> 19:31.960
show this sincerity.

19:33.720 --> 19:35.920
He was afraid I wouldn't like it before.

19:36.440 --> 19:38.310
But he's not afraid now?

19:40.960 --> 19:42.290
My heart belongs to you.

19:44.170 --> 19:46.100
My Lady, I don't think

19:46.400 --> 19:47.480
the Heir did it.

19:47.800 --> 19:49.000
I know he didn't do it.

19:49.750 --> 19:51.150
Someone wants me to think

19:51.440 --> 19:53.770
he killed her for her Phoenix Heart Token.

19:54.030 --> 19:56.490
Crown Prince Wenxi is
the hope of the people.

19:57.000 --> 19:58.790
Now that the token has appeared,

19:58.790 --> 20:01.790
Crown Prince Wenxi
should naturally reveal himself.

20:03.940 --> 20:05.670
Lejun, what are you doing here?

20:08.170 --> 20:10.300
I was just about to call you for dinner.

20:11.400 --> 20:12.640
I lost my earring,

20:13.110 --> 20:14.720
so I came out to look for it.

20:18.350 --> 20:19.590
Did you find it?

20:24.180 --> 20:24.900
But

20:24.960 --> 20:26.110
Xiao Wuyi and my mother are

20:26.110 --> 20:27.970
indeed hiding something from me.

20:28.070 --> 20:29.270
And my mother's death

20:29.920 --> 20:30.850
is related to it.

20:43.600 --> 20:46.750
It all started
because of Crown Prince Wenxi.

20:47.670 --> 20:50.290
[Memorial tablet of
the late Princess Li Yunzhao]

20:54.960 --> 20:56.590
Xie, why are you here?

20:57.360 --> 20:58.220
Your Highness.

21:00.440 --> 21:02.070
You agreed to let the entire estate

21:02.070 --> 21:03.200
mourn for my mother.

21:03.310 --> 21:04.070
I should

21:04.270 --> 21:05.400
thank you in person.

21:05.510 --> 21:06.910
It's the least I could do.

21:07.480 --> 21:09.510
Nanxing, take the things inside.

21:10.240 --> 21:10.680
Yes.

21:17.350 --> 21:18.210
Your Highness,

21:18.550 --> 21:20.160
you're also from the Capital.

21:20.160 --> 21:21.720
There are some things about the past

21:21.720 --> 21:22.920
that I want to ask you.

21:23.240 --> 21:23.960
Go ahead.

21:24.160 --> 21:25.270
I heard that my mother

21:25.270 --> 21:27.400
used to be very close to Empress Wenxi;

21:27.790 --> 21:28.920
close like sisters.

21:30.070 --> 21:30.680
Yes.

21:32.200 --> 21:33.830
The Two Beauties of the Capital

21:33.830 --> 21:35.160
referred to Empress Wenxi

21:35.160 --> 21:36.420
and Princess Yunzhao.

21:36.830 --> 21:37.920
I also heard

21:38.240 --> 21:39.270
that Old General Xiao

21:39.270 --> 21:42.160
used to be a groom
for Empress Wenxi's maternal family.

21:42.160 --> 21:44.880
He entered the Imperial Guard
because of Empress Wenxi's recommendation,

21:44.880 --> 21:46.030
and later led the Imperial Guard

21:46.030 --> 21:48.560
to escort the Ye royals and nobles
to the south

21:48.880 --> 21:50.110
Establishing Southern Ye

21:50.110 --> 21:51.350
and assisting the emperor,

21:51.350 --> 21:53.010
he was titled Prince Jing'an.

21:54.200 --> 21:55.070
That is true.

21:55.750 --> 21:56.550
But why didn't

21:56.550 --> 21:58.680
my mother ever mention the Xiao family

21:59.110 --> 22:00.880
or Old General Xiao to me?

22:05.920 --> 22:07.240
They were of different social classes.

22:07.240 --> 22:10.070
Not to mention the Prince
was just a groom back then.

22:10.070 --> 22:11.270
It's no surprise that

22:11.350 --> 22:13.200
the Princess didn't remember him.

22:13.200 --> 22:15.750
But Empress Wenxi could
entrust her last 50,000 Imperial Guards

22:15.750 --> 22:17.400
to Old General Xiao,
so he must've been

22:17.400 --> 22:18.600
a trusted confidant.

22:19.790 --> 22:22.590
My mother was also
someone Empress Wenxi trusted.

22:23.830 --> 22:25.360
How could she not remember?

22:27.310 --> 22:30.680
When Empress Wenxi gave birth
to the Crown Prince on the brink of death,

22:30.680 --> 22:32.030
for some unknown reason,

22:32.030 --> 22:34.160
the Crown Prince failed to appear
for a long time.

22:34.160 --> 22:35.920
So, the court was
divided into two factions.

22:35.920 --> 22:38.240
One faction insisted on
waiting for the Crown Prince to return

22:38.240 --> 22:39.830
and supporting the orthodox heir,

22:39.830 --> 22:40.960
such as your mother.

22:41.750 --> 22:43.790
The other faction was the various nobles,

22:43.790 --> 22:45.960
who advocated choosing
a prince of similar age

22:45.960 --> 22:47.550
from the royal clans

22:47.550 --> 22:49.010
and supporting him first.

22:49.030 --> 22:50.960
The two factions were deadlocked.

22:51.030 --> 22:52.590
Only Prince Jing'an,
who commanded the Imperial Guard,

22:52.590 --> 22:53.920
had the right to decide.

22:54.440 --> 22:55.970
The Prince chose the nobles

22:56.000 --> 22:57.530
and supported Emperor Rui,

22:57.590 --> 23:00.110
who is His Majesty's father.

23:01.640 --> 23:02.200
Yes.

23:03.000 --> 23:03.830
Since then,

23:04.030 --> 23:06.960
the Princess and the Xiao family
have had no contact.

23:07.310 --> 23:10.110
Then didn't the Prince
have a Phoenix Heart Token?

23:15.640 --> 23:16.920
I was just asking.

23:17.750 --> 23:18.440
Well...

23:19.310 --> 23:20.970
My mother's token is missing.

23:21.480 --> 23:23.510
Some say Xiao Wuyi killed my mother

23:25.750 --> 23:28.310
for her Phoenix Heart Token.

23:28.540 --> 23:29.210
That's why...

23:29.210 --> 23:29.940
Impossible.

23:30.920 --> 23:32.350
I can guarantee you that.

23:32.720 --> 23:34.980
Xiao Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.500
He couldn't...

23:46.960 --> 23:48.020
Please believe me.

23:48.550 --> 23:50.550
Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

23:51.640 --> 23:52.770
You must trust Wuyi.

23:52.880 --> 23:54.540
Don't let others mislead you.

23:56.550 --> 23:57.510
I understand.

23:59.510 --> 24:01.590
If you say so, I believe you.

24:03.110 --> 24:04.110
I trust Xiao Wuyi.

24:12.350 --> 24:13.000
Lady Xie,

24:13.480 --> 24:14.280
please tell me

24:15.070 --> 24:16.670
why you're bringing me here.

24:17.200 --> 24:18.160
Didn't I help you get

24:18.160 --> 24:20.000
the chance to compete in archery?

24:20.000 --> 24:21.310
You said you owed me a favor

24:21.310 --> 24:22.910
and would do one thing for me.

24:24.400 --> 24:25.240
I did say that.

24:25.720 --> 24:26.650
Then ask no more.

24:27.440 --> 24:28.960
I promise this matter

24:29.310 --> 24:31.040
doesn't violate the laws of Ye.

24:33.880 --> 24:35.880
Sir, here he is.

24:36.590 --> 24:38.050
Please hold out your hand.

24:59.550 --> 25:00.110
No.

25:02.890 --> 25:03.750
Thank you, sir.

25:04.110 --> 25:06.070
What exactly is going on?

25:06.510 --> 25:07.350
"No" what?

25:10.830 --> 25:11.480
Wuyi?

25:19.030 --> 25:19.750
You drew me.

25:20.720 --> 25:22.980
When was this? At the martial arts arena?

25:24.350 --> 25:25.480
The bone reader said

25:25.640 --> 25:28.170
you and Xiao Yao
aren't biological brothers.

25:28.270 --> 25:29.110
So sure, huh?

25:29.680 --> 25:30.810
What if he was wrong?

25:31.110 --> 25:32.590
The fact that you're sitting here

25:32.590 --> 25:33.880
proves that I'm right.

25:36.400 --> 25:37.070
When did you

25:37.070 --> 25:38.670
start doubting my identity?

25:39.480 --> 25:40.480
At Lingfeng Fort.

25:40.790 --> 25:41.450
That early?

25:42.960 --> 25:43.720
At first,

25:44.310 --> 25:46.160
I didn't care who Crown Prince Wenxi was.

25:46.160 --> 25:47.160
I only cared about

25:47.200 --> 25:48.530
who murdered my mother.

25:49.070 --> 25:50.480
I know my mother told you

25:51.350 --> 25:53.410
she'd trade the token for my freedom.

25:54.110 --> 25:55.570
The night before she died,

25:56.200 --> 25:57.510
I saw you two arguing.

25:58.440 --> 25:59.170
She wouldn't

25:59.510 --> 26:00.240
give this token

26:00.240 --> 26:02.500
to anyone other than Crown Prince Wenxi.

26:03.650 --> 26:04.980
Since she promised you,

26:05.350 --> 26:07.150
how could she go back on her word?

26:07.310 --> 26:08.710
That's why you suspected

26:09.790 --> 26:12.190
that I was the one
who attacked Her Highness

26:12.400 --> 26:13.350
to get the token?

26:14.350 --> 26:15.080
Besides you,

26:16.030 --> 26:17.960
Lejun was also a probable suspect.

26:18.070 --> 26:18.640
That day,

26:19.310 --> 26:21.550
I heard Her Highness arguing with someone.

26:21.550 --> 26:23.960
She said she knew the whereabouts
of Crown Prince Wenxi.

26:23.960 --> 26:25.620
She was going to give the token

26:26.110 --> 26:27.510
to Crown Prince Wenxi.

26:28.280 --> 26:29.610
In the carriage,

26:30.590 --> 26:32.880
I did give her a chance.

26:33.230 --> 26:34.830
But she knew your background

26:35.400 --> 26:38.860
and insisted on helping
Crown Prince Wenxi ascend the throne.

26:39.200 --> 26:40.240
If she heard my mother's desire

26:40.240 --> 26:42.110
to support Crown Prince Wenxi's ascension,

26:42.110 --> 26:44.170
it'd pose a threat to Mao's position.

26:44.640 --> 26:46.900
So she also had a reason
to take the token.

26:47.480 --> 26:48.810
Once Crown Prince Wenxi

26:49.030 --> 26:51.030
returns to Jiankang with the token,

26:51.590 --> 26:53.200
what will you do, Brother?

26:53.880 --> 26:55.210
For the Eastern Palace,

26:55.440 --> 26:57.070
you even gave up Yaoyao.

26:57.240 --> 26:59.440
I had to get rid of the ticking time bomb!

27:03.960 --> 27:05.790
Without Her Highness's token,

27:06.510 --> 27:08.400
even if Crown Prince Wenxi comes,

27:10.200 --> 27:12.200
the prophecy is considered broken.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.990
Who was she arguing with?

27:16.230 --> 27:18.640
I didn't see clearly, but I think...

27:19.920 --> 27:21.050
it must be Xiao Wuyi.

27:21.590 --> 27:23.450
Xiao Wuyi really wants the token.

27:23.880 --> 27:26.880
He's been holding on to Cui Jun's token.

27:27.510 --> 27:28.110
Brother.

27:29.160 --> 27:30.000
In my opinion,

27:30.550 --> 27:31.750
to Xiao Wuyi,

27:32.550 --> 27:35.000
you're just a pawn
kept in the imperial government

27:35.000 --> 27:36.800
to facilitate the Beifu Reform.

27:37.640 --> 27:39.830
If he dares to fall in love with Yaoyao,

27:40.550 --> 27:41.610
how much affection

27:42.110 --> 27:43.720
does he have left for you?

27:50.680 --> 27:51.680
You must never...

27:53.830 --> 27:55.200
trust Xiao Wuyi again.

27:58.590 --> 28:00.450
Only you have the grain that could

28:00.510 --> 28:01.510
drive a horse mad.

28:02.030 --> 28:02.920
So at first,

28:04.240 --> 28:05.840
I was more suspicious of you.

28:06.920 --> 28:08.160
When did it change?

28:16.550 --> 28:17.350
On the day of the wedding,

28:17.010 --> 28:19.050
[Ye Xing, a Shadow Envoy]

28:17.530 --> 28:19.530
the one who died was my twin brother.

28:19.560 --> 28:20.510
My brother and I were

28:20.510 --> 28:22.910
secret guards raised by Princess Yunzhao.

28:24.310 --> 28:25.510
Up until the wedding,

28:25.750 --> 28:26.750
our existence was

28:26.830 --> 28:28.630
unknown even to the Grand Tutor.

28:35.880 --> 28:36.960
Aren't you dead?

28:38.590 --> 28:40.160
Before Mother went to Lingfeng Fort,

28:40.160 --> 28:41.560
she sent him on an errand.

28:42.030 --> 28:43.550
But by the time he returned,

28:43.550 --> 28:45.080
Mother was already killed.

28:45.110 --> 28:47.330
When we entered the city that day,
I stayed behind

28:47.330 --> 28:48.590
just to tell Li Mao that

28:49.670 --> 28:50.870
I've found a witness.

28:51.830 --> 28:53.440
Lejun is severely injured and unconscious.

28:53.440 --> 28:54.480
If she wakes up,

28:54.920 --> 28:56.380
ask her to think carefully

28:56.680 --> 28:58.740
if there are any other witness clues.

28:59.510 --> 29:01.840
I had someone look for the groom's family,

29:02.400 --> 29:04.060
hoping to find some new clues.

29:04.340 --> 29:05.070
Then, My Lady

29:05.510 --> 29:06.790
ordered me to immediately take control

29:06.790 --> 29:07.880
of the groom's family

29:07.880 --> 29:09.030
and bring them to Jiankang,

29:09.030 --> 29:09.720
to see if anyone

29:09.720 --> 29:11.650
would take the opportunity to act.

29:11.720 --> 29:13.830
As expected, Prince Qi's men came.

29:15.190 --> 29:17.270
So you suspected Li Lejun early on.

29:18.030 --> 29:19.090
They took the bait.

29:19.960 --> 29:21.820
I just cast the hook for everyone.

29:22.590 --> 29:24.000
Luring the snake out of its hole

29:24.000 --> 29:25.260
also alerts the snake.

29:25.510 --> 29:26.590
Li Mao and Li Lejun

29:27.000 --> 29:28.680
must've noticed your suspicion,

29:28.680 --> 29:30.070
and will soon find out that

29:30.070 --> 29:30.750
the groom's family

29:30.750 --> 29:32.010
actually know nothing

29:32.510 --> 29:33.770
and aren't witnesses.

29:34.200 --> 29:35.440
So what if they know?

29:41.640 --> 29:42.200
Alright.

29:43.310 --> 29:44.340
Then let's talk about me.

29:44.340 --> 29:46.340
When exactly did I give myself away?

29:48.960 --> 29:51.680
When Cui Jun took my mother hostage.

29:52.160 --> 29:54.030
Crown Prince Wenxi died long ago!

29:54.030 --> 29:55.000
He didn't die!

29:57.350 --> 29:58.610
Cui Jun was taken away.

29:58.640 --> 30:00.960
The kidnapper left a message on the wall,
saying they were

30:00.960 --> 30:03.000
acting on Crown Prince Wenxi's orders.

30:03.000 --> 30:03.730
Impossible.

30:07.110 --> 30:08.440
Being overly certain is

30:09.200 --> 30:10.530
indeed inappropriate.

30:10.750 --> 30:12.080
Once suspicion arises,

30:12.590 --> 30:13.650
it can't be curbed.

30:14.510 --> 30:16.070
Xiyue Restaurant keeps telling stories

30:16.070 --> 30:17.830
about the token and Crown Prince Wenxi.

30:17.830 --> 30:19.400
If Crown Prince Wenxi is really alive,

30:19.400 --> 30:20.460
how old would he be?

30:20.590 --> 30:22.830
Twenty-four years ago... So, 24.

30:24.640 --> 30:26.880
The Dowager Princess's
contradictory attitude towards you...

30:26.880 --> 30:28.070
Wuyi is also my son.

30:29.590 --> 30:31.520
Then why refuse to go see Xiao Wuyi?

30:32.150 --> 30:34.410
Xiao Wuyi would never kill the Princess.

30:35.640 --> 30:37.370
And Mother's blind trust in you

30:37.750 --> 30:39.240
when she was at the Cui Mansion.

30:39.240 --> 30:40.570
Who says we stand alone?

30:40.720 --> 30:41.920
We share weal and woe.

30:42.510 --> 30:43.400
He indeed

30:43.400 --> 30:45.060
gave himself a very nice name.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.160
Also,

30:51.030 --> 30:53.160
her evaluation of Crown Prince Wenxi.

30:53.530 --> 30:55.070
Mother said Crown Prince Wenxi is

30:55.070 --> 30:56.510
someone who values the world

30:56.510 --> 30:57.720
more than himself,

30:57.880 --> 31:00.000
who spares no effort for this world,

31:00.400 --> 31:02.350
and that those who can bear this saying

31:02.350 --> 31:03.720
are few in this world.

31:06.640 --> 31:07.720
I happen to know

31:08.440 --> 31:09.970
a lunatic of such a caliber.

31:12.680 --> 31:13.440
Xie Jiayu,

31:14.590 --> 31:16.590
so you have such a high opinion of me.

31:17.270 --> 31:18.070
Xiao Wuyi,

31:19.080 --> 31:21.280
it's time to reveal your true identity.

31:23.270 --> 31:23.880
Yes.

31:26.890 --> 31:28.520
I am Crown Prince Wenxi.

31:32.200 --> 31:34.870
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

31:41.440 --> 31:43.170
It's time to bring Mother home.

31:43.790 --> 31:46.450
Nanxing, help me with
my grooming and dressing.

31:51.960 --> 31:52.960
Over the years,

31:53.200 --> 31:55.920
my Xie family had received so much favor
from the Princess.

31:55.920 --> 31:57.050
My Shanji Hall could

31:57.160 --> 31:58.790
stay open thanks to the Princess's

31:58.790 --> 32:00.270
years of financial support.

32:00.270 --> 32:01.550
These Buddhist scriptures were

32:01.550 --> 32:02.720
hand-copied by the women and children

32:02.720 --> 32:04.320
of Shanji Hall these few days

32:04.440 --> 32:06.000
to be offered to the Princess.

32:06.000 --> 32:07.440
Offer condolences!

32:09.720 --> 32:11.520
Princess Pingning has arrived.

32:15.200 --> 32:16.730
Greetings, Your Highness.

32:24.610 --> 32:27.090
My brother and I've had a tough life.

32:27.680 --> 32:30.010
Thankfully, the Princess took care of us.

32:30.480 --> 32:32.210
We're forever indebted to her.

32:32.400 --> 32:33.800
I have requested a decree

32:34.310 --> 32:36.110
to be an escort for the Princess.

32:53.110 --> 32:54.510
Greetings, Grand Tutor.

32:58.680 --> 33:00.740
Doing this even when you're injured.

33:01.400 --> 33:03.130
This is very thoughtful of you.

33:15.440 --> 33:16.720
It's time!

33:17.110 --> 33:19.720
Start the procession! Break the bowl!

33:23.880 --> 33:24.550
Wait!

33:37.750 --> 33:38.440
Father,

33:39.200 --> 33:40.060
with me around,

33:40.590 --> 33:42.320
how can my cousin break the bowl

33:42.530 --> 33:44.190
and an outsider be the escort?

33:51.640 --> 33:53.900
Lejun fell down the cliff with my mother,

33:54.440 --> 33:56.100
yet she recovered so quickly.

33:58.310 --> 33:59.070
It seems

34:00.200 --> 34:01.550
you're very blessed.

34:02.240 --> 34:04.920
Yaoyao, I'm sorry.

34:05.480 --> 34:07.280
I didn't hold onto the Princess.

34:07.480 --> 34:10.280
If only I had moved faster that day.

34:10.710 --> 34:12.590
Yaoyao, where have you been?

34:12.880 --> 34:14.400
It's been past the 7 days of mourning,

34:14.400 --> 34:16.550
and you haven't been
kneeling by the coffin.

34:16.550 --> 34:18.010
I forbade her from coming.

34:18.280 --> 34:20.050
I thought I made it very clear last time

34:20.050 --> 34:23.050
that you're not allowed to
set foot in the Xie Mansion!

34:37.150 --> 34:38.679
Everyone, you may not know,

34:39.070 --> 34:41.130
but my mother had divorced my father.

34:43.670 --> 34:44.710
Mother wouldn't want...

34:44.710 --> 34:45.190
Divorced?

34:45.190 --> 34:47.650
To be buried
in the Xie ancestral graveyard.

34:48.110 --> 34:49.030
So today,

34:50.190 --> 34:51.280
I'm here to take her away.

34:51.280 --> 34:52.080
How insolent!

34:52.360 --> 34:53.000
Jiayu,

34:53.480 --> 34:54.960
you can't just spout nonsense.

34:54.960 --> 34:56.960
How could your parents be divorced?

34:56.960 --> 34:58.560
I have two letters in my hand.

34:59.590 --> 35:00.450
This letter was

35:01.110 --> 35:03.480
written to me by my mother
when she left Jiankang.

35:03.480 --> 35:05.340
She said she'd divorced my father

35:05.360 --> 35:06.670
and wanted to go out to relax

35:06.670 --> 35:07.870
and travel the world.

35:08.230 --> 35:09.430
The second letter...

35:11.510 --> 35:12.760
was written to my father
when my mother was

35:12.760 --> 35:13.760
at Lingfeng Fort.

35:15.070 --> 35:17.200
These are the Princess's belongings.

35:20.460 --> 35:22.060
Unfortunately, she died

35:22.920 --> 35:24.320
before she could mail it.

35:25.360 --> 35:26.000
Father,

35:27.000 --> 35:28.060
want to take a look?

35:28.510 --> 35:29.550
No need.

35:31.590 --> 35:33.440
My marriage to your mother

35:34.110 --> 35:35.670
was decreed by the royals.

35:36.480 --> 35:39.070
So, without verification of the Clan Court

35:39.070 --> 35:40.360
and the approval of the Inner Court,

35:40.360 --> 35:41.710
your divorce paper is

35:42.280 --> 35:44.280
utterly invalid.

35:45.440 --> 35:47.960
Since the entire Xie family
is gathered here today,

35:47.960 --> 35:49.280
I will say it again:

35:50.990 --> 35:53.850
Xie Jiayu is not
Yunzhao's and my biological child!

35:55.150 --> 35:56.630
-What?
-What?

35:56.880 --> 35:57.900
-What's this?
-I don't know.

35:57.900 --> 35:59.130
She is just

35:59.880 --> 36:02.340
an orphan
Yunzhao picked up from somewhere.

36:03.320 --> 36:04.030
A little pet

36:04.030 --> 36:06.360
kept by Yunzhao for just over a decade.

36:07.760 --> 36:08.920
So, what right...

36:10.880 --> 36:12.210
What right does she have

36:12.670 --> 36:15.330
to make decisions for
my Xie family and Yunzhao?

36:15.480 --> 36:17.140
Let's not waste any more time.

36:19.110 --> 36:19.800
T-This...

36:34.360 --> 36:37.420
Did Prince Jing'an's Mansion
raise a bunch of bandits?

36:37.800 --> 36:39.630
Barging into my Xie mourning hall

36:39.630 --> 36:41.090
to snatch the coffin, huh?

36:41.590 --> 36:42.070
Is there

36:42.800 --> 36:44.230
still any law and order?

36:44.800 --> 36:45.530
Grand Tutor.

36:46.760 --> 36:48.030
Xie Jiayu's word is law

36:48.480 --> 36:49.280
today.

36:51.590 --> 36:54.320
I hope you can let Jiayu
finish what she has to say.

37:02.150 --> 37:04.280
Cui Jun is a secret spy of Northern Qin.

37:04.360 --> 37:05.960
After Mother was controlled by him,

37:05.960 --> 37:07.420
she had a chance to escape.

37:08.440 --> 37:10.590
But she heard Cui Jun
mention the An-Lu case.

37:10.590 --> 37:11.840
To pry the truth

37:11.840 --> 37:12.880
out of Cui Jun,

37:13.320 --> 37:15.520
Mother spared no effort to deal with him

37:15.760 --> 37:17.420
and almost couldn't get away.

37:18.360 --> 37:19.290
Mother knew that

37:19.400 --> 37:21.930
the An-Lu case was
a lifelong emotional burden of yours.

37:21.930 --> 37:23.600
You need closure.

37:24.840 --> 37:26.440
So she'd rather risk her life

37:27.280 --> 37:28.940
just to seek the truth for you.

37:29.760 --> 37:30.890
Mother once thought

37:31.030 --> 37:32.830
your obsessions were all wrong.

37:34.030 --> 37:36.400
Only later did she know she was wrong too.

37:37.320 --> 37:38.070
Now,

37:40.440 --> 37:41.770
the truth is in my hands.

37:49.110 --> 37:49.630
Yaoyao!

37:50.400 --> 37:50.800
Don't!

37:52.920 --> 37:53.650
Grand Tutor!

37:54.480 --> 37:55.150
I said to

37:55.800 --> 37:57.860
let Xie Jiayu finish speaking today.

38:02.150 --> 38:02.800
Father.

38:04.110 --> 38:05.510
My mother was murdered.

38:06.480 --> 38:08.150
Do you dare to let me investigate

38:08.150 --> 38:09.880
who really murdered my mother?

38:14.000 --> 38:16.280
Xie Jiayu, the nerve of you to say this.

38:17.320 --> 38:18.670
It was clearly because
the horse got spooked

38:18.670 --> 38:20.230
that your mother had that accidental fall.

38:20.230 --> 38:21.670
If you hadn't swapped carriages with her,

38:21.670 --> 38:23.360
it would've been you instead.

38:23.800 --> 38:24.760
What else is there to investigate?

38:24.760 --> 38:26.070
Fine, I understand.

38:27.480 --> 38:29.340
If you don't want to investigate,

38:30.670 --> 38:31.670
I'll do it myself.

38:33.070 --> 38:34.800
I'll get justice for my mother.

38:42.380 --> 38:43.980
Let me ask you again, Father.

38:44.030 --> 38:46.630
If I want to exchange the An-Lu case
for Mother,

38:47.110 --> 38:48.770
will you make the trade or not?

38:48.860 --> 38:50.410
No, no, you...

38:50.440 --> 38:51.110
Father.

38:52.010 --> 38:54.570
Will you make the trade or not?

39:02.110 --> 39:03.240
No! Don't, don't!

39:03.760 --> 39:07.030
If there's any truth
to the An-Lu case,

39:07.030 --> 39:09.230
then that's a matter of state!

39:09.800 --> 39:12.670
How can you jeopardize the state

39:13.150 --> 39:14.950
for your own selfish interests?

39:15.480 --> 39:16.080
Is that so?

39:17.230 --> 39:17.960
Then Father,

39:18.590 --> 39:20.070
in the repeating crossbow case,

39:20.070 --> 39:21.760
didn't you jeopardize the state

39:21.760 --> 39:22.880
for your own selfish interests?

39:22.880 --> 39:23.630
Nonsense!

39:23.840 --> 39:26.920
What does your father have to do
with the repeating crossbow?

39:26.920 --> 39:28.440
Whether I'm speaking nonsense,

39:28.440 --> 39:29.670
Father knows best.

39:30.210 --> 39:32.070
Whether I want to
burn everything down with me,

39:32.070 --> 39:33.400
Father also knows best.

39:35.800 --> 39:36.590
Mother told me

39:36.590 --> 39:37.800
your past stories.

39:40.710 --> 39:42.510
Since you love someone else,

39:43.110 --> 39:45.310
since even the beginning was a mistake,

39:45.360 --> 39:47.620
then why wouldn't you let Mother be free?

39:52.800 --> 39:54.460
From the Capital to Jiankang,

39:55.230 --> 39:56.290
too many people are

39:56.630 --> 39:58.630
trapped in the past and in the court.

39:59.150 --> 40:00.400
Mother is gone.

40:02.190 --> 40:03.070
I just want her

40:03.070 --> 40:04.800
to find peace in the afterlife.

40:06.400 --> 40:07.760
How could you—how could anyone—

40:07.760 --> 40:10.000
understand my love for Yunzhao?

40:11.360 --> 40:12.710
She was the one

40:13.070 --> 40:14.840
who chose the wrong beginning.

40:15.230 --> 40:15.960
Since it was wrong,

40:15.960 --> 40:17.820
then it must be wrong till the end.

40:18.000 --> 40:19.840
That's what she owed me.

40:25.000 --> 40:25.730
I'll trade!

40:26.480 --> 40:27.280
I'll trade.

40:32.360 --> 40:33.440
Mother was right.

40:34.670 --> 40:35.630
Nothing...

40:37.540 --> 40:39.070
can outweigh the An-Lu case

40:39.960 --> 40:41.400
in your heart.

40:51.760 --> 40:53.710
Today, the entire Xie family is here.

40:53.710 --> 40:55.070
Please be my witnesses.

40:55.800 --> 40:57.860
Mother wrote a divorce paper long ago,

40:57.860 --> 40:59.720
and Father has agreed to it today.

40:59.800 --> 41:00.460
From now on,

41:00.960 --> 41:04.160
Princess Yunzhao and the Xie family
have no further ties,

41:05.110 --> 41:06.170
parting amicably.

41:22.110 --> 41:23.070
Even if...

41:25.670 --> 41:27.670
you take Yunzhao away today,

41:28.400 --> 41:32.060
without the Emperor and Empress Dowager
annulling the marriage,

41:32.680 --> 41:34.230
she, Li Fuhua,

41:35.030 --> 41:36.670
will always be my wife!

41:36.670 --> 41:37.550
Her soul will

41:37.920 --> 41:40.320
never leave the Xie ancestral hall!

41:44.280 --> 41:46.680
You don't need to
worry about that, Father.

41:48.880 --> 41:49.480
Father.

41:52.550 --> 41:54.880
This is the last time
I'll call you Father.

42:13.050 --> 42:19.000
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

42:19.380 --> 42:24.750
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

42:25.570 --> 42:31.000
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

42:32.180 --> 42:37.000
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

42:38.910 --> 42:43.840
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong? ♪

42:45.320 --> 42:50.530
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

42:50.950 --> 42:54.510
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

42:54.530 --> 42:57.600
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

42:57.640 --> 43:03.020
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

42:59.460 --> 43:03.170
[Grand Tutor's Mansion]

43:03.220 --> 43:07.290
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

43:07.320 --> 43:10.290
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

43:10.310 --> 43:17.060
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪
